org.apache.flink.runtime.managementgraph

Class ManagementStage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.managementgraph.ManagementAttachment
      • org.apache.flink.runtime.managementgraph.ManagementStage

  • public final class ManagementStage
extends ManagementAttachment
    This class implements a management stage of a ManagementGraph. The stage is derived from an execution stage which is used in Nephele's internal scheduling structure.

    This class is not thread-safe.
